ion>\n    • UAL Corporation received a score of 88 for the second year in a row on the Human Rights Campaign 2009 Corporate Equality Index which rates large corporations on policies that affect their gay, lesbian, bisexual and transgender employees, consumers and investors. The HRC Corporate Equality Index rates companies on a scale of 0 to 100 percent. \n\n  </description>\n  <categories>\n    <category>\n      <category-name>Human Rights</category-name>\n    </category>\n  </categories>\n  <source>\n    <link><link-text>Green America: Company ID 401</link-text><url>http://www.greenamerica.org/programs/responsibleshopper/company.cfm?id=401</url><date>20111024164345</date></link>\n  </source>\n  <links>\n    <link><link-text>Human Rights Campaign</link-text><url>http://www.hrc.org/documents/HRC_Corporate_Equality_Index_2009.pdf</url><date></date></link><link><link-text>www.united.com</link-text><url>http://www.united.com</url><date></date></link>\n  </links>\n  <companies>\n   <company>\n      <normalized></normalized>\n      <tagged>United Airlines</tagged>\n      <address></address>\n      <GCPs></GCPs>\n    </company>\n  </companies>\n  <reviews>\n        <review><reviewer>insight</reviewer><date>20111023T171836Z</date></review>\n\n  </reviews>\n </evidence>'),('$VAR1 = [\n          bless( {\n                   \'URL\' => \'http://www.greenamerica.org/programs/responsibleshopper/company.cfm?id=391\',\n                   \'SourceText\' => \'Green America: Company ID 391\'\n                 }, \'Com::elle::bLeaf::EvidenceGenerator::NewsSource\' ),\n          \'The Nigerian government accepted an offer to settle its $5 billion lawsuit against Pfizer out of court.\'\n        ];\n',' <evidence>\n  <title>The Nigerian government accepted an offer to settle its $5 billion lawsuit against Pfizer out of court.</title>\n  <description>\n    The Nigerian government accepted an offer to settle its $5 billion lawsuit against Pfizer out of court.  The drug maker was being sued for punitive damages for allegedly illegally testing its antibiotic Trovan on children during a 1996 meningitis epidemic.  According to the Nigerian government and families of the victims, at least 96 children were either killed or suffered severe neurological injury as a result of the administration of the experimental drug.  A separate lawsuit filed in New York by the families was allowed to move forward in January 2009. \n\n  </description>\n  <categories>\n    <category>\n      <category-name>Human Rights</category-name>\n    </category>\n  </categories>\n  <source>\n    <link><link-text>Green America: Company ID 391</link-text><url>http://www.greenamerica.org/programs/responsibleshopper/company.cfm?id=391</url><date>20111024164346</date></link>\n  </source>\n  <links>\n    <link><link-text>Tide News</link-text><url>http://www.thetidenews.com/article.aspx?qrDate=01/28/2009&amp;qrTitle=Fed%20Govt,%20Pfizer%20opt%20for%20out-of-court%20settlement&amp;qrColumn=NATION</url><date></date></link><link><link-text>www.pfizer.com</link-text><url>http://www.pfizer.com</url><date></date></link>\n  </links>\n  <companies>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>pfizer inc./consumer health care</normalized>\n      <tagged>Pfizer</tagged>\n      <address></address>\n      <GCPs><GCP>0074300</GCP>\n<GCP>0086414</GCP>\n<GCP>0305012</GCP>\n<GCP>0305013</GCP></GCPs>\n    </company>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>pfizer inc./pfipharmecs div</normalized>\n      <tagged>Pfizer</tagged>\n      <address></address>\n      <GCPs><GCP>0071404</GCP></GCPs>\n    </company>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>pfizer inc.</normalized>\n      <tagged>Pfizer</tagged>\n      <address></address>\n      <GCPs><GCP>0087219</GCP></GCPs>\n    </company>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>pfizer consumer healthcare</normalized>\n      <tagged>Pfizer</tagged>\n      <address></address>\n      <GCPs><GCP>9310059</GCP></GCPs>\n    </company>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>pfizer consumer health products company