tish Airways check-in worker was suspended without pay for wearing a cross pendant around her neck.  The employee told an employment tribunal that the company had a ‘culture of hostility’ towards Christianity and did not give her faith equal treatment as the faiths of other employees.  Several months later, British Airways relaxed its rules concerning the display of religious symbols, and she was allowed to return to work. \n\n  </description>\n  <categories>\n    <category>\n      <category-name>Business Practices | Workers Rights</category-name>\n    </category>\n  </categories>\n  <source>\n    <link><link-text>Green America: Company ID 398</link-text><url>http://www.greenamerica.org/programs/responsibleshopper/company.cfm?id=398</url><date>20111024164415</date></link>\n  </source>\n  <links>\n    <link><link-text>Times (London)</link-text><url>http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/comment/faith/article2866171.ece</url><date></date></link><link><link-text>www.british-airways.com</link-text><url>http://www.british-airways.com</url><date></date></link>\n  </links>\n  <companies>\n   <company>\n      <normalized></normalized>\n      <tagged>British Airways</tagged>\n      <address></address>\n      <GCPs></GCPs>\n    </company>\n  </companies>\n  <reviews>\n        <review><reviewer>insight</reviewer><date>20111023T182827Z</date></review>\n\n  </reviews>\n </evidence>'),('$VAR1 = [\n          bless( {\n                   \'URL\' => \'http://www.greenamerica.org/programs/responsibleshopper/company.cfm?id=447\',\n                   \'SourceText\' => \'Green America: Company ID 447\'\n                 }, \'Com::elle::bLeaf::EvidenceGenerator::NewsSource\' ),\n          \"More than 100 people reported getting sick after eating at an Applebee\\x{2019}s restaurant near Syracuse, NY in March 2009.\"\n        ];\n',' <evidence>\n  <title>More than 100 people reported getting sick after eating at an Applebee’s restaurant near Syracuse, NY in March 2009.</title>\n  <description>\n