 styles of speech and manner of walking.&quot; The employee also used inappropriate language and hung nooses from his forklift. The man was suspended without pay for one month. \n\n  </description>\n  <categories>\n    <category>\n      <category-name>Politics</category-name>\n    </category>\n  </categories>\n  <source>\n    <link><link-text>Green America: Company ID 226</link-text><url>http://www.greenamerica.org/programs/responsibleshopper/company.cfm?id=226</url><date>20111024164425</date></link>\n  </source>\n  <links>\n    \n  </links>\n  <companies>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>ford motor co/parts   service</normalized>\n      <tagged>Ford Motor</tagged>\n      <address></address>\n      <GCPs><GCP>0031508</GCP>\n<GCP>0084422</GCP></GCPs>\n    </company>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>ford motor company/special vehicle oper.</normalized>\n      <tagged>Ford Motor</tagged>\n      <address></address>\n      <GCPs><GCP>0756122</GCP></GCPs>\n    </company>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>Ford Motor Company, S.A. De C.V.</normalized>\n      <tagged>Ford Motor</tagged>\n      <address>Av. Paseo De La Reforma No.333\nCol. Cuauhtemoc\n06500\nMexico City, D.F.\nMexico</address>\n      <GCPs><GCP>0714512</GCP></GCPs>\n    </company>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>Ford Motor Co/parts &amp; Service</normalized>\n      <tagged>Ford Motor</tagged>\n      <address>MI\nRoom 2130-D\n29500 Plymouth Road\n48150\nLivonia\nUnited States</address>\n      <GCPs><GCP>0084424</GCP></GCPs>\n    </company>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>Ford Motor Co/parts &amp; Service</normalized>\n      <tagged>Ford Motor</tagged>\n      <address>MI\nRoom 2130-D\n29500 Plymouth Road\n48150\nLivonia\nUnited States</address>\n      <GCPs><GCP>0084424</GCP></GCPs>\n    </company>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>Ford Motor Co/parts &amp; Service</normalized>\n      <tagged>Ford Motor</tagged>\n      <address>MI\nRoom 2130-D\n29500 Plymouth Road\n48150\nLivonia\nUnited States</address>\n     