a measurement and rating o</title>\n  <description>\n    The Health Care Quality Report, published annually by the California Office of the Patient Advocate, is a measurement and rating on how well a medical group provides care and services to its patients and how the patients rate it. In the 2010 ranking Aetna scored three stars out of three possible on both Meeting National Standards of Care and Members rating of HMO (Health Maintenance Organization). \n\n  </description>\n  <categories>\n    <category>\n      <category-name>Human Rights | Health and Wellness</category-name>\n    </category>\n  </categories>\n  <source>\n    <link><link-text>Green America: Company ID 424</link-text><url>http://www.greenamerica.org/programs/responsibleshopper/company.cfm?id=424</url><date>20111024164449</date></link>\n  </source>\n  <links>\n    <link><link-text>California Office of the Patient Advocate</link-text><url>http://www.opa.ca.gov/report_card/hmorating.aspx </url><date></date></link>\n  </links>\n  <companies>\n   <company>\n      <normalized></normalized>\n      <tagged>Aetna</tagged>\n      <address></address>\n      <GCPs></GCPs>\n    </company>\n  </companies>\n  <reviews>\n        <review><reviewer>insight</reviewer><date>20111023T203444Z</date></review>\n\n  </reviews>\n </evidence>'),('$VAR1 = [\n          bless( {\n                   \'URL\' => \'http://www.greenamerica.org/programs/responsibleshopper/company.cfm?id=230\',\n                   \'SourceText\' => \'Green America: Company ID 230\'\n                 }, \'Com::elle::bLeaf::EvidenceGenerator::NewsSource\' ),\n          \'Basel Action Network (BAN) is a group dedicated to preventing the \"globilization of the toxic chemicals crisis.\"  In a 2005 report\'\n        ];\n',' <evidence>\n  <title>Basel Action Network (BAN) is a group dedicated to preventing the &quot;globilization of the toxic chemicals crisis.&quot;  In a 2005 report</title>\n  <description>\n    Basel Action Network (BAN) is a group dedicated to preventing the &quot;globilization of the toxic chemicals crisis.&quot;  In a 2005 report entitled “The Digital Dump: Exporting Re-use and Abuse to Africa,” BAN examines the current downside to the information technology growth in the industrialized world, focusing on the environmental ramifications in Lagos, Nigeria. The study demonstrates how Nigeria, representative of developing nations, has disproportionately carried the burden of toxic cyber waste. The formal and informal dumps have leached dangerous toxins, such as dioxins, polycyclic aromatic hydrocarbons, and heavy metals, into the air and groundwater. Gateway products were among those found “washed up” on the West African import market. \n\n  </description>\n  <categories>\n    <category>\n      <category-name>Environment</category-name>\n    </category>\n  </categories>\n  <source>\n    <link><link-text>Green America: Company ID 230</link-text><url>http://www.greenamerica.org/programs/responsibleshopper/company.cfm?id=230</url><date>20111024164450</date></link>\n  </source>\n  <links>\n    <link><link-text>Basel Action Network</link-text><url>http://www.ban.org/BANreports/10-24-05/documents/TheDigitalDump.pdf</url><date></date></link><link><link-text>www.gateway.com</link-text><url>http://www.gateway.com</url><date></date></link>\n  </links>\n  <companies>\n   <company>\n      <normalized></normalized>\n      <tagged>Gateway</tagged>\n      <address></address>\n      <GCPs></GCPs>\n    </company>\n  </companies>\n  <reviews>\n        <review><reviewer>insight</reviewer><date>20111023T203521Z</date></review>\n\n  </reviews>\n </evidence>'),('$VAR1 = [\n          bless( {\n                   \'URL\' => \'http://www.greenamerica.org/programs/responsibleshopper/company.cfm?id=207\',\n                   \'SourceText\' => \'Green America: Company ID 207\'\n                 }, \'Com::elle::bLeaf::EvidenceGenerator::NewsSource\' ),\n          \'In January 2007 a California judge granted class-action status to a gender discrimination lawsuit brought forward by Costco employ\'\n        ];\n',' <evidence>\n  <title>In January 2007 a California judge granted class-action status to a gender discrimination lawsuit brought forward by Costco employ</title>\n  <description>\n    In January 2007 a California judge granted class-action status to a gender discrimination lawsuit brought forward by Costco employees alleging that qualified females were routinely passed over for promotion.  More than 700 women claim to have been denied promotions based on their gender. \n\n  </description>\n  <categories>\n    \n  </categories>\n  <source>\n    <link><link-text>Green America: Company ID 207</link-text><url>http://www.greenamerica.org/programs/responsibleshopper/company.cfm?id=207</url><date>20111024164450</date></link>\n  </source>\n  <links>\n    \n  </links>\n  <companies>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>costco companies inc.</normalized>\n      <tagged>Costco</tagged>\n      <address></address>\n      <GCPs><GCP>0096619</GCP></GCPs>\n    </company>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>Costco Companies Inc.</normalized>\n      <tagged>Costco</tagged>\n      <address>WA\n999 Lake Drive\n98027\nIssaquah\nUnited States</address>\n      <GCPs><GCP>0096619</GCP></GCPs>\n    </company>\n  </companies>\n  <reviews>\n        <review><reviewer>insight</reviewer><date>20111023T203540Z</date></review>\n\n  </reviews>\n </evidence>'),('$VAR1 = [\n          bless( {\n                   \'URL\' => \'http://www.greenamerica.org/programs/responsibleshopper/company.cfm?id=238&MajorSub=1&CompanyName=Zero\',\n                   \'SourceText\' => \'Green America: Company ID 238\'\n                 }, \'Com::elle::bLeaf::EvidenceGenerator::NewsSource\' ),\n          \'In 2008 Fortune magazine reported that Hershey is not playing a direct role in reforming the cocoa industry in the Ivory Coast, wh\'\n        ];\n',' <evidence>\n  <title>In 2008 Fortune magazine reported that Hershey is not playing a direct role in reforming the cocoa industry in the Ivory Coast, wh</title>\n  <description>\n    In 2008 Fortune magazine reported that Hershey is not playing a direct role in reforming the cocoa industry in the Ivory Coast, which is plagued by child labor practices and other labor violations.  Instead, Hershey (and the cocoa industry in general) contributes to the International Cocoa Initiative (ICI), which is supposed to address labor issues in the Ivory Coast.  However, critics maintain that the ICI has only provided one staff member in the Ivory Coast and has done little to end child labor. \n\n  </description>\n  <categories>\n    <category>\n      <category-name>Business Practices | Workers Rights</category-name>\n    </category>\n  </categories>\n  <source>\n    <link><link-text>Green America: Company ID 238</link-text><url>http://www.greenamerica.org/programs/responsibleshopper/company.cfm?id=238&amp;MajorSub=1&amp;CompanyName=Zero</url><date>20111024164451</date></link>\n  </source>\n  <links>\n    <link><link-text>CNN Money</link-text><url>http://money.cnn.com/2008/01/24/news/international/chocolate_bittersweet.fortune/</url><date></date></link>\n  </links>\n  <companies>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>the hershey company</normalized>\n      <tagged>Hershey</tagged>\n      <address></address>\n      <GCPs><GCP>0034000</GCP></GCPs>\n    </company>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>hershey\'s chocolate world</normalized>\n      <tagged>Hershey</tagged>\n      <address></address>\n      <GCPs><GCP>0032284</GCP></GCPs>\n    </company>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>hershey creamery company</normalized>\n      <tagged>Hershey</tagged>\n      <address></address>\n      <GCPs><GCP>0024682</GCP></GCPs>\n    </company>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>The Hershey Company</normalized>\n      <tagged>Hershey</tagged>\n      <address>PA\n100 Crystal A Dr\n17033\nHershey\nUnited States</address>\n      <GCPs><GCP>0034000</GCP></GCPs>\n    </company>\n   <company>\n      <no