B\n60179 \nHoffman Estates\nUnited States</address>\n      <GCPs><GCP>0883967</GCP></GCPs>\n    </company>\n  </companies>\n  <reviews>\n        <review><reviewer>insight</reviewer><date>20111023T215742Z</date></review>\n\n  </reviews>\n </evidence>'),('$VAR1 = [\n          bless( {\n                   \'URL\' => \'http://www.greenamerica.org/programs/responsibleshopper/company.cfm?id=221\',\n                   \'SourceText\' => \'Green America: Company ID 221\'\n                 }, \'Com::elle::bLeaf::EvidenceGenerator::NewsSource\' ),\n          \'ExxonMobil confirmed that its greenhouse gas emissions rose two percent in 2003 to 135.6 million tons.\'\n        ];\n',' <evidence>\n  <title>ExxonMobil confirmed that its greenhouse gas emissions rose two percent in 2003 to 135.6 million tons.</title>\n  <description>\n    ExxonMobil confirmed that its greenhouse gas emissions rose two percent in 2003 to 135.6 million tons. Exxon’s worsening emissions may be caused, in part, by an increase of flaring of gas in Nigeria. Flaring, which is illegal in most countries, is when natural gas is extracted simultaneously with oil and burned off straight into the atmosphere. Exxon\'s emissions are more than 50 percent higher than their closest competitor\'s, despite only a slightly larger production of oil and gas. \n\n  </description>\n  <categories>\n    \n  </categories>\n  <source>\n    <link><link-text>Green America: Company ID 221</link-text><url>http://www.greenamerica.org/programs/responsibleshopper/company.cfm?id=221</url><date>20111024164518</date></link>\n  </source>\n  <links>\n    <link><link-text>Ethical Corporation</link-text><url>http://www.ethicalcorp.com</url><date></date></link>\n  </links>\n  <companies>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>exxon company, u.s.a.</normalized>\n      <tagged>Exxon</tagged>\n      <address></address>\n      <GCPs><GCP>0077162</GCP></GCPs>\n    </company>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>Exxon Company, U.S.A.</normalized>\n      <tagge