get, Costco and Procter &amp; Gamble. \r\nOrganic Consumers Association has also recently released a report on brands that have sharply reduced levels of 1,4-dioxane since March 2008 that include 365 Everyday Value (Whole Foods), Earth Friendly Products, Ecco Bella, Giovanni, Jason, Johnson &amp; Johnson, Kiss My Face, Life Tree, Method, Nature’s Gate, Planet Ultra, and Seventh Generation. \n\n  </description>\n  <categories>\n    <category>\n      <category-name>Human Rights | Health and Wellness</category-name>\n    </category>\n  </categories>\n  <source>\n    <link><link-text>Green America: Company ID 259</link-text><url>http://www.greenamerica.org/programs/responsibleshopper/company.cfm?id=259&amp;MajorSub=1&amp;CompanyName=Victoria%27s%20Secret%20%28Limited%20Brands%20subsidiary%29</url><date>20111024164538</date></link>\n  </source>\n  <links>\n    <link><link-text>USA Today</link-text><url>http://http://www.usatoday.com/news/health/2009-03-12-formaldehyde_N.htm</url><date></date></link><link><link-text>www.limitedbrands.com</link-text><url>http://www.limitedbrands.com</url><date></date></link>\n  </links>\n  <companies>\n   <company>\n      <normalized></normalized>\n      <tagged>365 Everyday Value</tagged>\n      <address></address>\n      <GCPs></GCPs>\n    </company>\n   <company>\n      <normalized></normalized>\n      <tagged>Bath &amp; Body Works</tagged>\n      <address></address>\n      <GCPs></GCPs>\n    </company>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>CVS, Inc.</normalized>\n      <tagged>CVS</tagged>\n      <address>NC\n4403 Lebanon Rd\n28227\nCharlotte\nUnited States</address>\n      <GCPs><GCP>0734468</GCP></GCPs>\n    </company>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>CVS Pharmacy, Inc.</normalized>\n      <tagged>CVS</tagged>\n      <address>RI\n1 CVS Drive\n02895\nWoonsocket\nUnited States</address>\n      <GCPs><GCP>0050428</GCP></GCPs>\n    </company>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>costco companies inc.</normalized>\n      <tagged>Costco</tagged>\n 