urce>\n    <link><link-text>Green America: Company ID 392</link-text><url>http://www.greenamerica.org/programs/responsibleshopper/company.cfm?id=392</url><date>20111024164607</date></link>\n  </source>\n  <links>\n    <link><link-text>PR Newswire</link-text><url>http://www.pr-inside.com/shame-on-merck-drug-giant-blasted-r615736.htm</url><date></date></link>\n  </links>\n  <companies>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>merck pharmaceutical (hk) ltd</normalized>\n      <tagged>Merck</tagged>\n      <address></address>\n      <GCPs><GCP>4897016</GCP></GCPs>\n    </company>\n  </companies>\n  <reviews>\n        <review><reviewer>insight</reviewer><date>20111023T225133Z</date></review>\n\n  </reviews>\n </evidence>'),('$VAR1 = [\n          bless( {\n                   \'URL\' => \'http://www.greenamerica.org/programs/responsibleshopper/company.cfm?id=229&MajorSub=1&CompanyName=Old%20Navy\',\n                   \'SourceText\' => \'Green America: Company ID 229\'\n                 }, \'Com::elle::bLeaf::EvidenceGenerator::NewsSource\' ),\n          \'In 2002, <I>BusinessWeek</I> named Gap as having one of the worst corporate boards.\'\n        ];\n',' <evidence>\n  <title>In 2002, &lt;I&gt;BusinessWeek&lt;/I&gt; named Gap as having one of the worst corporate boards.</title>\n  <description>\n    In 2002, &lt;I&gt;BusinessWeek&lt;/I&gt; named Gap as having one of the worst corporate boards. The company was cited for inside deals including contracts with the chairman\'s brother to build and remodel stores and a consulting arrangement with the  chairman\'s wife. The magazine also pointed out the interlocking directorship with the Gap\'s CEO sitting on Apple\'s board and Apple\'s CEO sitting on Gap\'s. \n\n  </description>\n  <categories>\n    \n  </categories>\n  <source>\n    <link><link-text>Green America: Company ID 229</link-text><url>http://www.greenamerica.org/programs/responsibleshopper/company.cfm?id=229&amp;MajorSub=1&amp;CompanyName=Old%20Navy</url><date>2011102416460