    Marriott International announced in May 2010 that it will invest $500,000 over the next two years to support a water conservation program in China. The program will help protect the largest source of fresh water on the planet, found in the mountains of Southwest China. The hotel chain is currently working on reducing its water and energy use by 25 percent by 2017. Marriott has also demonstrated corporate social responsibility in the area as it raised more than $3 million to help provide disaster relief when the May 2008 earthquake struck, taking the lives of nearly 70,000 people. The chain currently operates 45 hotels in China, with more than 25 hotels being planned or under construction. \n\n  </description>\n  <categories>\n    <category>\n      <category-name>Human Rights</category-name>\n    </category>\n  </categories>\n  <source>\n    <link><link-text>Green America: Company ID 438</link-text><url>http://www.greenamerica.org/programs/responsibleshopper/company.cfm?id=438</url><date>20111024164629</date></link>\n  </source>\n  <links>\n    <link><link-text>PR Newswire</link-text><url>http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/marriott-international-launches-water-conservation-program-in-china-94714449.html </url><date></date></link>\n  </links>\n  <companies>\n   <company>\n      <normalized></normalized>\n      <tagged>Marriott International</tagged>\n      <address></address>\n      <GCPs></GCPs>\n    </company>\n  </companies>\n  <reviews>\n        <review><reviewer>insight</reviewer><date>20111023T234642Z</date></review>\n\n  </reviews>\n </evidence>'),('$VAR1 = [\n          bless( {\n                   \'URL\' => \'http://www.greenamerica.org/programs/responsibleshopper/company.cfm?id=278\',\n                   \'SourceText\' => \'Green America: Company ID 278\'\n                 }, \'Com::elle::bLeaf::EvidenceGenerator::NewsSource\' ),\n          \'The Ethical Trading Action Group (ETAG), in association with Maquila Solidarity Network (MSN) and AccountAbi