obs, or 4 percent of its workforce.</title>\n  <description>\n    In early 2009, Macy\'s, Inc announced plans to cut 7,000 jobs, or 4 percent of its workforce.  While no stores are expected to close, the layoffs will affect about 40 percent of executive positions in addition to 5,100 jobs in the chain\'s 850 stores.  The cuts come in response to slumping retail sales and the tumultuous economic environment. \n\n  </description>\n  <categories>\n    <category>\n      <category-name>Business Practices | Workers Rights</category-name>\n    </category>\n  </categories>\n  <source>\n    <link><link-text>Green America: Company ID 222</link-text><url>http://www.greenamerica.org/programs/responsibleshopper/company.cfm?id=222</url><date>20111024164645</date></link>\n  </source>\n  <links>\n    <link><link-text>Daily Business Review</link-text><url>http://www.bizjournals.com/albany/stories/2009/02/02/daily8.html</url><date></date></link>\n  </links>\n  <companies>\n   <company>\n      <normalized>macy\'s</normalized>\n      <tagged>Macy\'s Inc</tagged>\n      <address></address>\n      <GCPs><GCP>0023495</GCP></GCPs>\n    </company>\n  </companies>\n  <reviews>\n        <review><reviewer>insight</reviewer><date>20111024T001719Z</date></review>\n\n  </reviews>\n </evidence>'),('$VAR1 = [\n          bless( {\n                   \'URL\' => \'http://www.greenamerica.org/programs/responsibleshopper/company.cfm?id=406\',\n                   \'SourceText\' => \'Green America: Company ID 406\'\n                 }, \'Com::elle::bLeaf::EvidenceGenerator::NewsSource\' ),\n          \"\\x{2022} T-Mobile International employees in Germany, Austria, Great Britain, and the Netherlands are members of trade or labor unions.\"\n        ];\n',' <evidence>\n  <title>• T-Mobile International employees in Germany, Austria, Great Britain, and the Netherlands are members of trade or labor unions.</title>\n  <description>\n    • T-Mobile International employees in Germany, Austria, Great Britain, and